### SendStatus -> 7 events in Generous verbosity
###
### REQUIRES:
###   1. 02_TrackLoad.http run first so loadNumber 999001 exists in Tracking
###   2. VerifyTrackingAccount needs partnerid=143, accountid=4Ly94/tNcLoELyhI1+6WXA==
###      These match TTTrackingPartnerID / TTTrackingAccountID hardcoded in
###      WebCallFunctions.cs. Use real TT credentials when testing against real TT
###      callback traffic.
###   3. Required SP-side fields: ltExternalId, driverPhone (else AddWithValue drops
###      the parameter and spStatusLoadTracking_Insert errors).

POST http://localhost:5129/api/truckertoolstracking/SendStatus
